# Built payloads: re-include the directory so git descends into it (the parent `payloads/*`
# rule above would otherwise stop traversal). The file-level keep/ignore rules live in
# payloads/.gitignore (meta.json + build_*.sh + quantize_*.py + *.md kept; binaries ignored).
!payloads/built/

